{"word":"ναυσθλόω","slug":"ναυσθλόω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ναυσθλόω</b></el> <el>(ναυσθλόω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:contracted, contraction'>contr.</a> for <a href='S:ναυστολέω'><el>ναυστολέω</el></a>\n<p/><i>to carry by sea</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to take with one by sea</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to go by sea</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/>"}]}